caller_intent: Vicky Hill needs a copy of her insurance declaration page for her employer, as a previous attempt to obtain it was unsuccessful.
resolution_steps: Heather asks for Vicky's policy number, address, and email to verify her account.
Heather confirms the request is for a declaration page showing coverages.
Heather assures Vicky the document will be sent within five minutes and instructs her to call back if it's not received within ten minutes.
knowledge_required: Process for retrieving and sending insurance declaration pages
summary: Vicky Hill requested a copy of her Travelers insurance declaration page for her employer. Heather collected verification details and committed to sending the document within five minutes, with a follow-up instruction if it was not received within ten minutes.
